replies.body:
Swain is the very first champion I mained... and I have to admit I really do not like this updated look..... I was hoping that they would update "slightly" or just update the abilities. NOw it seems to me that the core essence of Swain that touched my heart is gone. The art, the ability, the skinny crippled guy with a bird on his shoulder, hiding behind the mask mysteriously, saying "my bird is hungry"... The guy who's limping with no way to dash out yet exploding rage on R when the time comes. The W that gave him a way to escape...etc. ARGGGG.. i feel ROBBED ;(

I wish there is a way I can keep the current swain.... seriously.... but I can't. 

{{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}}
